Subject: Worker Job

& [WorkerJob_codex_cli_worker] is a turn-spool worker record
  + [worker_id] is codex_cli_worker
  + [lane] is codex_cli
  + [objective] is Additional Codex CLI worker lane for bounded job packets.
  + [status] is deferred
  + [prompt_packet] is prompt.md
  + [launch_command] is deferred: explicit launch policy required
  + [result_file] is result.sop
  + [attention_frame] is none
  = must: inspect launch_command before execution
  - never: infer completion from launch alone
